# {{project_name}}

Tessera plugin crate.

## Usage

Add the plugin to your Tessera app:

```toml
[dependencies]
{{project_name}} = { path = "{{project_name}}" }
```

Register it in your entrypoint (recommended):

```rust
tessera_ui::entry! {
    // ...
    packages = [
        {{project_name_snake}}::HelloPackage::default(),
    ],
    // ...
}
```

You can also register the plugin directly:

```rust
tessera_ui::entry! {
    // ...
    plugins = [
        {{project_name_snake}}::HelloPlugin::default(),
    ],
    // ...
}
```

Use it from components or app code:

```rust
{{project_name_snake}}::with_plugin(|plugin| {
    println!("{}", plugin.message());
});
```

## Build

```bash
cargo build
```
